# Styling Guide

The NexusAI website uses Tailwind CSS for styling with custom CSS variables and classes.

## Key Style Elements

### Fonts
- Primary font: 'Inter' for body text
- Secondary font: 'Orbitron' for headings and emphasis (class: `orbitron`)

### Colors
- Background: Dark theme with black/dark gray backgrounds
- Accent colors: Gradient from blue to purple to pink
- Text: White and light gray for readability on dark backgrounds

### Special Effects
- Gradient text (class: `gradient-text`)
- Glowing elements (class: `glow`)
- Card glow effect (class: `card-glow`)
- Hero gradient background (class: `hero-gradient`)
- Pulse animation (class: `pulse-animation`)
- Grid pattern background (class: `grid-pattern`)

### Terminal Component
- Terminal container (class: `terminal`)
- Terminal header (class: `terminal-header`)
- Terminal body (class: `terminal-body`)
- Blinking cursor effect (class: `blink`)
